snippet.title: Christ Is King - Barron Trump Sings
snippet.description:
Christ Is King

Check us out on Spotify! https://open.spotify.com/album/3y1CZVxPBVqYl2ljdNVWno?si=lLRWLYbeQcuXD9TQDeKi7A

⬇️⬇️⬇️ Watch more videos below! ⬇️⬇️⬇️
https://youtu.be/WBHJZs8ZeFQ
https://youtu.be/GAdihLnAiXk
https://youtu.be/SZZW8YMZlMg?si=kP7ZE5s5fhhjjpX2
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hq_JjAodbY0

Verse 1
I’ve walked through halls of power, I’ve seen the world’s parade
Gold and glory all around, but none of it has stayed
I’ve heard the lies and whispers, the pressure and the sting
But none of that can shake me — I know who is my King

Pre-Chorus
They talk of crowns and thrones of men
But I know what will never end

Chorus
Christ is King, over every nation
Ruler high, beyond imagination
Through the storm, through the fire and flame
He remains, He forever reigns
All I am, I lay at His feet
Christ is King — He is all I need

Verse 2
My name was born in headlines, my face in every frame
But titles fade like shadows, and glory’s not my aim
They look at me like legacy, a symbol or a sign
But I belong to Heaven, and victory divine

Pre-Chorus
I’m not ashamed, I speak His name
In every trial, He remains

Chorus
Christ is King, over every nation
Ruler high, beyond imagination
Through the storm, through the fire and flame
He remains, He forever reigns
All I am, I lay at His feet
Christ is King — He is all I need

Bridge
Not by might, not by power
But by His grace in this very hour
I’ll stand tall, I won’t retreat
With Jesus walking next to me

Final Chorus
Christ is King, let the people sing
Every heart, every voice, everything
From the towers to the dusty roads
He is risen, He alone knows
All I am, I give Him control
Christ is King — He reigns in my soul

Outro
Yes, Christ is King... forever on the throne
I am His — and I am not alone
